The_Velvet_Sheep presents - four fabulous bands on a friday night in a legendary venue , with music ranging from gothic - tinged alternative rock to widescreen cinema pop via ethereal cold - wave . Plus a late bar . Most excellent ...
This event is lovingly brought to you by ' The_Velvet_Sheep presents ' , and will take place at :
Hope and Anchor_Live
207 Upper_St , Islington , London N1 1RL
Which is a 2 minute walk to the underground station : Highbury & Islington on the Victoria_Line
Bus routes : Day : 4 , 19 , 30 , 43 , 153 , 393
24 hours : 19 , 43 , 271 & 277
Tickets are just £ 5 online or £ 6 on the door
